snippet.title: என் தங்கச்சியா இது 🥺❤️ Papa’s Transformation ❣️ என் கண்ணே பட்டுரும் போல 😭❤️| @ramwithjaanu
snippet.description:
Hey Deys! Today's vlog is all about pampering our sisters, and let me tell you, it was no easy feat! We had an absolute blast. Jaanu  did makeup for our dear papa. This video is a rehearsal makeup session for her upcoming puberty function. As if that wasn't enough, we couldn't contain our laughter while engaging in some science experiments. You can catch the full video on KEERTHI SHRATHAH CHANNEL, and trust me, you won't want to miss out on any of the fun. Prepare to have your funny bone tickled throughout the entire video. It's not just about vlogging; we were creating cherished memories along the way.
Hope you have enjoyed watching this video.

snippet.title: Dhoomam - Malayalam Trailer | Fahadh Faasil | Aparna | Pawan Kumar | Vijay Kiragandur| Hombale Films

Audio On Hombale Music

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 53 Teaser - 8th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 53 Teaser - 8th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.description:
#weather #monsoon #cyclone #biparjoy 

અરબી સમુદ્રમાં બની રહેલી સિસ્ટમ વાવાઝોડામાં પરિવર્તિત થઈ રહી છે. જોકે તેનો રસ્તો કયો હશે અને તે કઈ તરફ આગળ વધશે એ અંગે હવામાન વિભાગ દ્વારા અનુમાન જાહેર કરાયું છે. તો વાવાઝોડું ખરેખર કંઈ દિશામાં આગળ વધશે અને ક્યાં જઈને ટકરાશે?

snippet.title: क्यों है Gokuldham की पुरुष मंडली परेशान? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | FE 1522 | 6 June 2023
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony Pal: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Episode 1522:
----------------------
The men finally clean the premises and are relieved. The effects of strenuous work are showing and Jethalal feels tired. Meanwhile, Popatlal thanks the ladies for making them clean their respective houses. 

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 1522
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा  #sonypal 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G1DSZ-26hoFNNWQ9Jnu9kZu

snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 52 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 52 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 8th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim

Agha Mustafa

snippet.description:

Tere Bin Episode 51 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream - 7th June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Nisa Hair Removal Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Director: Siraj ul Haq

snippet.title: മരണത്തിന് തൊട്ട്മുൻപ് ചുറുചുറുക്കോടെ വേദിയിൽ തമാശ പറഞ്ഞും പൊട്ടി ചിരിച്ചും സുധി ബിനു അടിമാലിക്കൊപ്പം
snippet.description:
Comedian Kollam Sudhi's car collided with a pickup van at Kaipamangalam in Thrissur while returning to Kochi after participating in a stage show in Vadakara, Kozhikode.

കോഴിക്കോട് വടകരയിൽ നടന്ന 24 കണക്ടിന്റെ സ്റ്റേജ് ഷോയിൽ പങ്കെടുത്ത് തിരികെ കൊച്ചിയിലേക്ക് മടങ്ങും വഴിയായിരുന്നു ഹാസ്യതാരം കൊല്ലം സുധി സഞ്ചരിച്ചിരുന്ന കാർ തൃശ്ശൂർ കൈപ്പമംഗലത്ത് വച്ച് വാഹനം പിക്കപ്പ് വാനുമായി കൂട്ടിയിടിക്കുന്നത്. | Kollam sudhi Death

snippet.title: Jetha ने क्यों दी Bagha और Nattu Kaka को Party? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Jetha Chala US
snippet.description:
Click here  to Subscribe to the LIV Comedy channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpEhnqL0y41EpW2TvWAHD7Q?sub_confirmation=1

Jetha has to leave for America in next three days. Bagha and Nattu Kaka celebrate this and ask Jetha to give them a party. Jetha orders Pizza and French fries for them. He calls Bapuji to tell the news but Nattu Kaka stops him from doing so. Jetha thinks he had such a good day just because of Babita Ji as she told him have a nice day. 

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 3547
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3792 | 8 June 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3792: Bohot Sara Khaana
--------------------------------------------------------
After Kalpana's departure, Sapna arrives at the same restaurant. Pyaarelal greets Sapna with the same flower that Kalpana had given him. Sapna shows her romantic gestures, and she holds Pyaarelal's hands, which makes him ecstatic. Anjali makes a fake call from Pyaarelal's office, Toofan Express, and tells him to report immediately. Sapna gets upset about Pyaarelal's departure, so she requests that he meet her again at 6 p.m. Pyaarelal changes his attire to blue because this time he will be visiting Kalpana again. So Pyaarelal changes his outfit in the car. When Pyaarelal reaches Sapna's place, Anjali and Komal have already arrived. How will Pyaarelal juggle his double life now? Stay tuned!

snippet.description:
Rise of the Beasts is “the best Transformers movie yet.” See it on the biggest screen possible this Thursday. Watch the final trailer now.

Returning to the action and spectacle that have captured moviegoers around the world, Transformers: Rise of the Beasts will take audiences on a ‘90s globetrotting adventure with the Autobots and introduce a whole new faction of Transformers – the Maximals – to join them as allies in the existing battle for earth. snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3791 | 7 June 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3791: Pyaarelal Ke Bahane
--------------------------------------------------------
Popatlal receives a call from Kalpana, who invites him to a date at the "Love Bird Garden" restaurant. Pyaarelal, also known as Popatlal, tells Sapna that he needs to take an urgent leave to attend an office meeting. Pyaarelal meets with Anjali and Komal outside Sapna's house to plan a meeting with both of these girls at the same time. Anjali decides to call Pyaarelal's office after half an hour to leave Kalpana and meet Sapna. How will Pyaarelal handle the conflicting dates? Is he going to get caught? Watch the show to find out more!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3791, 7 June 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

శుక్రవారం, 2023 జూన్ 2 సాయంత్రం దాదాపు 7 గంటల సమయంలో మూడు రైళ్లు ప్రమాదానికి గురయ్యాయి. అయితే ఇంత పెద్ద ప్రమాదం ఎలా జరిగిందనేదానిపై ఇప్పటికీ ఎన్నో ప్రశ్నలు.. వాటన్నింటికీ సమాధానం ఇది.
#Odisha #TrainAccident #CoromandelExpress
___________

snippet.description:
EXPEND4BLES – Only In Theaters September 22. Starring Jason Statham, Curtis “50 Cent” Jackson, Megan Fox, Dolph Lundgren, Tony Jaa, Iko Uwais, Randy Couture, Jacob Scipio, Levy Tran, with Andy Garcia, and Sylvester Stallone.

https://twitter.com/expendables
https://www.tiktok.com/@lionsgate ​​

#EXPEND4BLES

A new generation of stars join the world’s top action stars for an adrenaline-fueled adventure in Expend4bles. Reuniting as the team of elite mercenaries, Jason Statham, Dolph Lundgren, Randy Couture, and Sylvester Stallone are joined for the first time by Curtis “50 Cent” Jackson, Megan Fox, Tony Jaa, Iko Uwais, Jacob Scipio, Levy Tran, and Andy Garcia. Armed with every weapon they can get their hands on and the skills to use them, The Expendables are the world’s last line of defense and the team that gets called when all other options are off the table. But new team members with new styles and tactics are going to give “new blood” a whole new meaning.

►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

snippet.title: 지민 (Jimin) '편지 (Dear. ARMY)' Live Clip #2023BTSFESTA
snippet.description:
#지민 #Jimin #편지 #Dear_ARMY

✍️ Lyrics
What should I say 
And how should I say it
I’m not so good at this

I know it may seem cliché
But I’ll try not to make it sound so light 
As I convey these words

I say oh oh 
I want you to be happier
Whenever I stumbled and fell
You, who reached out your hand to me

I say oh oh 
Now I’ll be the one to hold you up
Whenever you wanna cry
So you won’t fall

Even after time passes by
Will we stay the same?
Just like when we first met

If you and I are together
Even the desert can turn into a sea
Just like the way we used to be

I say oh oh 
I hope this lasts forever
When I was lost in the cold winter
You came to me like a warm spring day

I say oh oh 
I will always cherish
The relationship between us
And the moments we filled it with

Baby, don’t leave
Just stay by my side, yeah
You who saw someone much greater in me than myself
To give you in return everything you have given me
And to keep my promises to you 

Don’t you worry 
By your side I’ll always stay, yeah
Though we don’t know what lies ahead
It can be scary, it can be daunting  
But never forget that we are together

I know it may seem cliché
But I’ll try not to make it sound so light 
As I convey these words

snippet.title: I am Disappointed - New Honda Elevate SUV | ICN Studio
snippet.description: So we finally witnessed the global debut of its compact SUV - Honda Elevate - in India today. With this Honda has become one of the last ones to enter the segment, but that's not all. It also misses out on many features that a lot of its rivals offer. Also, it will only get a single 1.5-litre i-VTEC engine that we have seen in the City as well. But sadly, it won't get the sophisticated strong hybrid tech that the City has. Instead, the company will launch its electric version by 2026.

snippet.title: Cyclone Biparjoy: અરબી સમુદ્રના વાવાઝોડાનો રૂટ નક્કી થઈ ગયો, ગુજરાત પર આવશે આ વાવાઝોડું?
snippet.description:
#weather #monsoon #cyclone 
અરબી સમુદ્રમાં બની રહેલી સિસ્ટમ વાવાઝોડામાં પરિવર્તીત થઈ રહ્યું છે. અને હવે હવામાન વિભાગે આપેલી માહિતી પ્રમાણે તેનો રસ્તો પણ નક્કી થઈ ગયો છે. જો કે તે આગળ કઈ બાજુ ફંટાશે તે હજુ પણ પ્રશ્ન બનેલો છે.  તેવામાં આ વાવાઝોડું ગુજરાત પર આવશે કે ફંટાઈ જશે એ મોટો સવાલ છે કારણ કે ગુજરાતમાં બરાબર ચોમાસાની એન્ટ્રી પહેલા જ આ વાવાઝોડું અરબી સમુદ્રમાં આકાર લઈ રહ્યું છે. તો ગુજરાતના ચોમાસા પર આની શું અસર થશે એની માહિતી જુઓ અમારા આ વીડિયોમાં.

વીડિયો - દીપક ચુડાસમા, ઍડિટ - સુમિત વૈદ

તમે અમારી સાથે જોડાઈ શકો છો :

snippet.description:

Episode 3790: Pyaarelal Under Pressure
--------------------------------------------------------
Sapna contacts Pyaarelal and tells him that she adores him as well. Pyaarelal is overjoyed and decides to meet with her. Sapna invites Pyaarelal to her home, but Pyaarelal prefers to speak with her privately, so they plan to walk outdoors thereafter. Pyaarelal invites Taarak and Anjali to accompany him to Sapna's place. Taarak declines Payaarelal's request since his boss will not give him any time off. As a result, Anjali and Komal decide to follow Pyaarelal on his visit to Sapna's house. Pyaarelal is taken aback by Sapna's parents' generosity, but much more so when he meets Sapna's uncle. What made Pyaarelal afraid of Sapna's uncle?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3790, 6 June 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About the show:

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.title: Apple WWDC 2023 keynote in 26 minutes
snippet.description:
Apple just finished up its annual Worldwide Developers Conference keynote, where it made some of the biggest announcements it’s ever made at the event, including its Vision Pro mixed reality headset and a bigger 15-inch MacBook Air. Plus, the Mac Studio and Mac Pro get an upgrade with a more powerful M2 Ultra chip. We also got a look at new updates for iOS and iPadOS, including interactive widgets. Here’s everything you missed. #Apple #WWDC #Technology

Read more: https://trib.al/6fqFRDg
